      <bpmn2:documentation id="_c7STI1_7EfGRstmrwDP8aA"><![CDATA[Find a CAGE under the deployed cpeCrossId via CROSS PROJECT API. (FIND - depends on created cpeCrossId)]]></bpmn2:documentation>
